values: yesterday and today have been truly horrible and i have like no one to comfort me or even listen to me bitch. i feel kinda alone and unwanted like the smelly kid in class. things in my life are going really bad for me, this includes classes and work and my social life and just my life. i've tried like everything to make it better but each problem just hinders the next. today all i wanted was a hug and i couldn't even get that. sometimes i feel like i'm not even in control of my life and i'm just going through the phases. something needs to happen. maybe it's just me though maybe my lifestyle isn't what others want it to be or maybe people are just getting bored of me. whatever the case is, it doesn't feel good. is it bad that today at work i seriously almost bawled my eyes out cuz i felt so alone? i just want a hug and for some one to tell me everything will be fine, but not just like a fake hug i want like a genuine "i'm concerned" hug. i think that would make me feel a whole lot better, knowing that someone else is concerned about my life and not just me.

anyway that's my day hopefully tomorrow will be better.
